This paper deals with image understanding and semantic embeddings, which are topics commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques such as classification and embedding learning, which fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on the ImageNet dataset, which is commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
